I created an end-to-end full-stack app for signing and handling digital agreements on a custom blockchain. Frontend: stateful React + TypeScript (Vite) with secure state, auth, wallet integration, and signing/viewing UI. Backend: Node.js + Express for off-chain computation, user storage, APIs, and blockchain bridging. On-chain: Substrate Rust parachain on Polkadot with an "agreements" pallet (storage, events, extrinsics). Showcases full-stack and blockchain engineering expertise.